### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@token = {{login.response.body.$.data.token}}

### Health
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/health

### Login
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "admin123"
}

### Me
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### KB list
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/kb/items?page=1&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### KB create (batch)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/kb/items
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "items": [
    { "title": "示例新闻A", "content": "正文...", "source_name": "测试源", "published_at": "2024-12-01T10:00:00Z", "tags": ["测试","样例"] },
    { "title": "示例新闻B", "content": "正文...", "source_name": "测试源", "published_at": "2024-12-01T11:00:00Z", "tags": ["测试"] }
  ]
}

### Semantic search
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/search/semantic
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "query": "AI 医疗 最新应用",
  "top_k": 5
}

### QA
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/search/qa
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "query": "AI 在医疗影像的作用",
  "top_k": 5
}

### Analytics keywords
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/analytics/keywords?top=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
